data.description: Seller is motivated! So come see your future dream home located in the heart of Deltona! This Spacious 3/2 on the lake has it all! Built in 2004 and recently remodeled between 2021-2022. This beauty features both a large screened in front porch & back patio. Fully updated kitchen with stone countertops, new appliances, reverse osmosis water filtration system at kitchen sink, remodeled bathrooms, Luxury Flooring, water softener system. 2 car attached garage, along with a rock pad that can accommodate 15+ cars, fit two large RVs, and/or any other toys! New roof also done within the last year! House is turn key ready for ADT alarm system. Including glass break sensors on all windows/sliding doors. Conveniently located about 35 min from Orlando, and 35-40 min from Daytona & New Smyrna Beach.  (*Room dimensions are estimated. Buyer to confirm exact dimensions*)    Furniture can also be included with reasonable offers! (Kitchen and living room sets. Including almost new Couches, 2 California King beds, Dining table w/Chairs).    Currently occupied by a tenant on a Month-to-month lease. Tenant only needs 30 days notice to vacate.
